This distribution contains example programs and applets from the book
_Java in a Nutshell_, by David Flanagan.  The examples are written by
David Flanagan, and are Copyright (c) 1996 by O'Reilly & Associates.

The file index.html contains much more information about the examples.
Please view it with your web browser.

The examples are organized by chapter, and are found in the
subdirectories section1/ through section9/.

To order _Java in a Nutshell_, call 1-800-889-8969 from the USA or
Canada, or +1-707-829-0515 from other countries.
